PrecisOrder confirming a request made to three Members of Parliament to travel to Kiev, Ukraine, from November 28th to December 5th, 1991, in order to observe the unfolding of the referendum on the question of independence and the presidential elections. (1) PATRICK BOYER, (2) ROSS HARVEY, and (3) Dr. REY PAGTAKHAN
Attachments
